gameRecap.title: Game Recap: Nuggets 125, Pelicans 113
gameRecap.excerpt: The Nuggets defeated the Pelicans, 125-113. Nikola Jokic put up his 12th triple-double of the season as he recorded 27 points (11-17 FG), 10 rebounds and 14 assists for the Nuggets, while Jamal Murray added 20 points, nine assists and three 3PM in the victory. Zion Williamson tallied a game-high 30 points, along with 6 rebounds and five assists for the Pelicans in the losing effort. The Nuggets improve to 27-13 on the season, while the Pelicans fall to 23-16.
